      Pharmacist. <span class="text-primary-600">Artist</span>. Dreamer.
    </h2>
    <div class="mt-10 sm:mx-auto sm:w-full sm:max-w-4xl">
      <img class="rounded-xl" src="img/laura_painting_w_sushi.jpg" alt="me painting in my studio with my cat sushi watching over me" />
    </div>
    <main class="mt-10 sm:mx-auto sm:w-full sm:max-w-md">
      <blockquote class="rounded-r-md border-l-4 border-primary-600 bg-primary-50 text-primary-900 p-4">
