      <blockquote class="mt-8 rounded-r-md border-l-4 border-primary-600 bg-primary-50 text-primary-900 p-4">
        "Over time, we recognize the patterns that dampen that feeling of coming alive and we work to loosen the threads they are woven of. We go through times when our perspectives dramatically shift, when our assumptions are deeply challenged. When we see new possibilities or sense that what has held us back from freedom, creativity, or new adventures, could actually be left behind.‚Äù 
        <span class="block mt-2 italic">- Real Life by Sharon Salzberg</span>
      </blockquote>
